        <div class="inline-cta">
          <div class="cta-copy">
            <h4>Don't want another SEO tool to learn?</h4>
            <p>theStacc handles audits, content, publishing, GBP, and rank tracking — without you ever opening a dashboard. <strong>Try it for $1</strong>, cancel anytime.</p>
