        <h2 id="performance">Performance benchmarks — how Frase stacks up</h2>
        <p>Frase's data extraction quality is strong. SERP scraping is accurate, brief assembly is fast, and the GSC integration just works. The weaknesses are downstream — AI writing output and ranking correlation.</p>

